  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Cleric Domain Power</strong><br/><br/><p>As a move action, a triadic priest can share one teamwork feat she has with up to two bonded companions that are within 10 feet of her. Her bonded companions do not need to meet the feat's prerequisites and gain the benefits of the feat for 1 round plus 1 additional round for every 5 class levels the triadic priest has. A bonded companion can gain only one teamwork feat in this way at a time. The triadic priest can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + her Wisdom modifier.</p>",
